title: The new questline doesn't progress
body: After winning a game with the Domination tree the game doesn't give me a win for the quest.

replies.body:
I've seen a lot of reports of this mission not being correctly updated recently, but it does seem like it was eventually being pushed through for most so far! Let me know if you still aren't seeing this mission completed at all and I can take another look.

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}
